{"title": "Song of Smoke",
"body": ["To watch you walk", "cross the room in your black", "corduroys is to see", "civilization start\u2014", "the", "-", "-", "of your strut is flint", "striking rock\u2014the spark", "of a length of cord", "rubbed till", "smoke starts\u2014you stir", "me like coal", "and for days smoulder.", "I am no more", "a Boy Scout and, besides,", "could never", "put you out\u2014you", "keep me on", "all day like an iron, out", "of habit\u2014", "you threaten, brick-", "house, to burn", "all this down. You leave me", "only a chimney."],
