{"title": "Woman Watches Ocean on a Reef through a Glass-Bottomed Boat",
"body": ["In the ocean one fish", "swallows the other:", "a geometric progression of", "loss.", "You are bigger than I.", "The calamity of love", "swelling out larger than us.", "And what destiny partakes of", "our dilemma?", "Swallows the cause and effect:", "eyes and kissing mouths and enlarged", "parts wanting to breathe and wanting.", "There is no gentle sense to this.", "Is there?", "Only a kind of terror", "at the chain", "of events, the scale of loss, the ordered", "destruction one against the other\u2014", "all that something larger", "awaits its moment."],
