{"title": "Language Lesson 1976",
"body": ["When Americans say a man", "takes liberties, they mean", "he\u2019s gone too far. In Philadelphia today I saw", "a kid on a leash look mom-ward", "and announce his fondest wish: one", "bicentennial burger, hold", "the relish. Hold is forget,", "in American.", "On the courts of Philadelphia", "the rich prepare", "to serve, to fault. The language is a game as well,", "in which love can mean nothing,", "doubletalk mean lie. I\u2019m saying", "doubletalk with me. I\u2019m saying", "go so far the customs are untold.", "Make nothing without words,", "and let me be", "the one you never hold."],
