{"title": "Last Wish",
"body": ["A long time have I known you... Why,", "Full eighteen years, I must confess!", "All pink are you; pale, blear am I.", "Winters, mine; yours, spring\u2019s comeliness!", "White cemetery lilacs sprout", "Over my temples; but soon, now,", "The grove entire will bloom about", "My head, to shade my withered brow.", "Pallid, my sun sinks low, and will", "Soon fade on the horizon\u2019s face;", "And on the mournful, doleful hill", "I see my final dwelling-place.", "Oh! May you from your lips let fall", "A kiss, too long delayed, upon", "My own, so that beneath my pall", "I may rest, heart at peace, anon..."],
