{"title": "Eve Revisited",
"body": ["Pomegranates fell from the trees", "in our sleep. If we stayed", "in the sun too long", "there were aloes", "to cool the burn.", "Henbane for predators", "and succulents when the rain was scarce.", "There was no glorified past", "to point the way", "true and natural", "for the sexes to meet.", "He kept looking to the heavens", "as if the answer were anywhere", "but here. I was so bored", "with our goodness", "I couldn\u2019t suck the juice", "from one more pear.", "It\u2019s", "I kept telling him,", "rooted in the soil", "like every other tree", "you know. And I wove us", "a bed of its uppermost branches."],
