{"title": "Domestic Situation",
"body": ["Maybe you\u2019ve heard about this. Maybe not.", "A man came home and chucked his girlfriend\u2019s cat", "In the wood chipper. This really happened.", "Dinner wasn\u2019t ready on time. A lot", "Of other little things went wrong. He spat", "On her father, who came out when he learned", "About it. He also broke her pinky,", "Stole her checks, and got her sister pregnant.", "But she stood by him, stood strong, through it all,", "Because she loved him. She loved him, you see.", "She actually said that, and then she went", "And married him. She felt some unique call.", "Don\u2019t try to understand what another", "Person means by love. Don\u2019t even bother."],
