{"title": "Lines Depicting Simple Happiness",
"body": ["The shine on her buckle took precedence in sun", "Her shine, I should say, could take me anywhere", "It feels right to be up this close in tight wind", "It feels right to notice all the shiny things about you", "About you there is nothing I wouldn\u2019t want to know", "With you nothing is simple yet nothing is simpler", "About you many good things come into relation", "I think of proofs and grammar, vowel sounds, like", "A is for knee socks, E for panties", "I is for buttondown, O the blouse you wear", "U is for hair clip, and Y your tight skirt", "The music picks up again, I am the man I hope to be", "The bright air hangs freely near your newly cut hair", "It is so easy now to see gravity at work in your face", "Easy to understand time, that dark process", "To accept it as a beautiful process, your face"],
