{"title": "The Horse Fell Off the Poem",
"body": ["The horse fell off the poem", "and the Galilean women were wet", "with butterflies and dew,", "dancing above chrysanthemum", "The two absent ones: you and I", "you and I are the two absent ones", "A pair of white doves", "chatting on the branches of a holm oak", "No love, but I love ancient", "love poems that guard", "the sick moon from smoke", "I attack and retreat, like the violin in quatrains", "I get far from my time when I am near", "the topography of place ...", "There is no margin in modern language left", "to celebrate what we love,", "because all that will be ... was", "The horse fell bloodied", "with my poem", "and I fell bloodied", "with the horse\u2019s blood ..."],
