{"title": "Heart",
"body": ["My heart was suspect.", "Wired to an EKG,", "I walked a treadmill", "that measured my ebb", "and flow, tracked isotopes", "that ploughed my veins,", "looked for a constancy", "I\u2019ve hardly ever found.", "For a month I worried", "as I climbed the stairs", "to my office. The mortality", "I never believed in", "was here now. They", "say my heart\u2019s ok,", "just high cholesterol, but", "I know my heart\u2019s a house", "someone has broken into,", "a room you come back", "to and know some stranger", "with bad intent has been there", "and touched all that you love. You know", "he can come back. It\u2019s his call,", "his house now."],
