{"title": "This Room",
"body": ["The room I entered was a dream of this room.", "Surely all those feet on the sofa were mine.", "The oval portrait", "of a dog was me at an early age.", "Something shimmers, something is hushed up.", "We had macaroni for lunch every day", "except Sunday, when a small quail was induced", "to be served to us. Why do I tell you these things?", "You are not even here."],
