{"title": "Spare Parts",
"body": ["We barge out of the womb", "with two of them: eyes, ears,", "arms, hands, legs, feet.", "Only one heart. Not a good", "plan. God should know we", "need at least a dozen,", "a baker\u2019s dozen of hearts.", "They break like Easter eggs", "hidden in the grass,", "stepped on and smashed.", "My own heart is patched,", "bandaged, taped, barely", "the same shape it once was", "when it beat fast for you."],
