{"title": "\"How can I keep my maidenhead\"",
"body": ["How can I keep my maidenhead,", "My maidenhead, my maidenhead;", "How can I keep my maidenhead,", "Among sae mony men, O.", "The Captain bad a guinea for\u2019t,", "A guinea for\u2019t, a guinea for\u2019t,", "The Captain bad a guinea for\u2019t,", "The Colonel he bad ten, O.", "But I\u2019ll do as my minnie did,", "My minnie did, my minnie did,", "But I\u2019ll do as my minnie did,", "For siller I\u2019ll hae nane, O.", "I\u2019ll gie it to a bonie lad,", "A bonie lad, a bonie lad;", "I\u2019ll gie it to a bonie lad,", "For just as gude again, O.", "An auld moulie maidenhead,", "A maidenhead, a maidenhead;", "An auld moulie maidenhead,", "The weary wark I ken, O.", "The stretchin\u2019 o\u2019t, the strivin\u2019 o\u2019t,", "The borin o\u2019t, the rivin\u2019 o\u2019t,", "And ay the double drivin o\u2019t,", "The farther ye gang ben, O."],
