{"title": "\"Weep You No More, Sad Fountains\"",
"body": ["Weep you no more, sad fountains;", "What need you flow so fast?", "Look how the snowy mountains", "Heaven\u2019s sun doth gently waste.", "But my sun\u2019s heavenly eyes", "View not your weeping,", "That now lie sleeping", "Softly, now softly lies", "Sleeping.", "Sleep is a reconciling,", "A rest that peace begets.", "Doth not the sun rise smiling", "When fair at even he sets?", "Rest you then, rest, sad eyes,", "Melt not in weeping", "While she lies sleeping", "Softly, now softly lies", "Sleeping."],
