"body": ["Kiss\u2019d yestreen, and kiss\u2019d yestreen,", "Up the Gallowgate, down the Green:", "I\u2019ve woo\u2019d wi\u2019 lords, and woo\u2019d wi\u2019 lairds,", "I\u2019ve mool\u2019d wi carles and mell\u2019d wi\u2019 cairds,", "I\u2019ve kiss\u2019d wi\u2019 priests\u2014 \u2018twas done i\u2019 the dark,", "Twice in my gown and thrice in my sark;", "But priest, nor lord, nor loon can gie", "Sic kindly kisses as he gae me."],
