{"title": "\"Behold, the grave of a wicked man\"",
"body": ["Behold, the grave of a wicked man,", "And near it, a stern spirit.", "There came a drooping maid with violets,", "But the spirit grasped her arm.", "\u201cNo flowers for him,\u201d he said.", "The maid wept:", "\u201cAh, I loved him.\u201d", "But the spirit, grim and frowning:", "\u201cNo flowers for him.\u201d", "Now, this is it \u2014", "If the spirit was just,", "Why did the maid weep?"],
"region": "",
