{"title": "Confession of a Stolen Kiss",
"body": ["My ghostly fader, I me confess,", "First to God and then to you,", "That at a window, wot ye how,", "I stale a kosse of gret swetness,", "Which don was out avisiness\u2014", "But it is doon, not undoon, now.", "My ghostly fader, I me confess,", "First to God and then to you.", "But I restore it shall, doutless,", "Agein, if so be that I mow;", "And that to God I make a vow,", "And elles I axe foryefness.", "My ghostly fader, I me confesse,", "First to God and then to you."],
