{"title": "First Farewell to J.G.",
"body": ["Farewell my dearer half, joy of my heart,", "Heaven only knows how loth I am to part:", "Whole Months but hours seem, when you are here,", "When absent, every Minute is a Year:", "Might I but always see thy charming Face,", "I\u2019de live on Racks, and wish no easier place.", "But we must part, your Interest says we must;", "Fate, me no longer with such Treasure trust.", "I wou\u2019d not tax you with Inconstancy,", "Yet", ", you are not so kind as I:", "No Interest, no nor Fate it self has pow\u2019r", "To tempt me from the Idol I adore:", "But since you needs will go, may", "be", "Kinder to you, than", "is to me:", "May all you meet and every thing you view", "Give you such Transport as I met in you.", "May no sad thoughts disturb your quiet mind,", "Except you\u2019l think of her you left behind."],
