{"title": "Love's Witness",
"body": ["Slight unpremeditated Words are borne", "By every common Wind into the Air;", "Carelessly utter\u2019d, die as soon as born,", "And in one instant give both Hope and Fear:", "Breathing all Contraries with the same Wind", "According to the Caprice of the Mind.", "But", "are constant Witnesses,", "Substantial Records to Eternity;", "Just Evidences, who the Truth confess,", "On which the Lover safely may rely;", "They\u2019re serious Thoughts, digested and resolv\u2019d;", "And last, when Words are into Clouds devolv\u2019d."],
