{"title": "Once We Played",
"body": ["Once we played at love together\u2014", "Played it smartly, if you please;", "Lightly, as a windblown feather,", "Did we stake a heart apiece.", "Oh, it was delicious fooling!", "In the hottest of the game,", "Without thought of future cooling,", "All too quickly burned Life\u2019s flame.", "In this give-and-take of glances,", "Kisses sweet as honey dews,", "When we played with equal chances,", "Did you win, or did I lose?"],
