{"title": "Of Love",
"body": ["How Love came in, I do not know,", "Whether by th\u2019 eye, or eare, or no:", "Or whether with the soule it came", "(At first) infused with the same:", "Whether in part \u2018tis here or there,", "Or, like the soule, whole every where:", "This troubles me: but as I well", "As any other, this can tell;", "That when from hence she does depart,", "The out-let then is from the heart."],
