{"title": "Natural Law",
"body": ["If you press a stone with your finger,", "Sir Isaac Newton observed,", "The finger is also", "Pressed by the stone.", "But can a woman, pressed by memory\u2019s finger,", "In the deep night, alone,", "Of her softness move", "The airy thing", "That presses upon her", "With the whole weight of love? This", "Sir Isaac said nothing of."],
