{"title": "Mythmaking on the Merritt Parkway",
"body": ["Aluminum sky. Only November", "Leaks into early frost", "Like a ruptured jug", "Of gas. I\u2019d rather hold", "Onto this road with pliers", "Than have another face of you", "Frisk my heart. Cool hands,", "The touch of every moon", "Is crucial and incomplete", "As a sponge bath. Leaving", "A backbone of lights", "Behind me, a blinking string", "Of pelts in fox country,", "I long to slice through", "Connecticut\u2019s middle, marbled", "And pink as medium-rare beef.", "I dream you."],
