{"title": "The Echo Elf Answers",
"body": ["How much shall I love her?", "For life, or not long?", "\u201cNot long.\u201d", "Alas! When forget her?", "In years, or by June?", "\u201cBy June.\u201d", "And whom woo I after?", "No one, or a throng?", "\u201cA throng.\u201d", "Of these shall I wed one", "Long hence, or quite soon?", "\u201cQuite soon.\u201d", "And which will my bride be?", "The right or the wrong?", "\u201cThe wrong.\u201d", "And my remedy \u2013 what kind?", "Wealth-wove, or earth-hewn?", "\u201cEarth-hewn.\u201d"],
