{"title": "When to Her Lute Corinna Sings",
"body": ["When to her lute Corinna sings,", "Her voice revives the leaden strings,", "And doth in highest notes appear", "As any challenged echo clear;", "But when she doth of mourning speak,", "Ev\u2019n with her sighs the strings do break.", "And as her lute doth live or die,", "Let by her passion, so must I:", "For when of pleasure she doth sing,", "My thoughts enjoy a sudden spring,", "But if she doth of sorrow speak,", "Ev\u2019n from my heart the strings do break."],
