{"title": "Virginity",
"body": ["One must be brave to live through", "a day. What remains", "is nothing but the pleasure of longing\u2014very precious.", "Longing", "purifies as does flying, strengthens as does an effort,", "it fashions the soul", "as work", "fashions the belly.", "It is like an athlete, like a runner", "who will never", "stop running. And this", "gives him endurance.", "Longing", "is nourishing for the strong.", "It is like a window", "on a high tower, through which", "blows the wind of strength.", "Longing,", "Virginity of happiness."],
