19s dark ink in your last smile", "where the stars have swallowed their train schedule", "where the stars have drowned in their dark petticoats", "like a sock of hamburger", "receiving the lightning", "into his clitoris", "red on red the prisoner", "confesses his waltz", "through the corkscrew lightning", "nevermind the lightning", "in your teeth let\u2019s waltz", "I am the hashish pinball machine", "that rapes a piano."],
