{"title": "The Garden of Love",
"body": ["I went to the Garden of Love,", "And saw what I never had seen:", "A Chapel was built in the midst,", "Where I used to play on the green.", "And the gates of this Chapel were shut,", "And Thou shalt not. writ over the door;", "So I turn'd to the Garden of Love,", "That so many sweet flowers bore.", "And I saw it was filled with graves,", "And tomb-stones where flowers should be:", "And Priests in black gowns, were walking their rounds,", "And binding with briars, my joys & desires."],
