{"title": "Sorrow",
"body": ["Sorrow like a ceaseless rain", "Beats upon my heart.", "People twist and scream in pain, \u0097", "Dawn will find them still again;", "This has neither wax nor wane,", "Neither stop nor start.", "People dress and go to town;", "I sit in my chair.", "All my thoughts are slow and brown:", "Standing up or sitting down", "Little matters, or what gown", "Or what shoes I wear."],
